import React from 'react'
import ProductDetails from './ProductDetails'

function ProductContainer() {
  return (
    <main>
        <section className='products'>
                <ProductDetails
                ProductName = ""
                ProductImage = ""
                ProductDescription = ""
                Product
                />
                <ProductDetails/>
                <ProductDetails/>
                <ProductDetails/>
                <ProductDetails/>
                <ProductDetails/>
                <ProductDetails/>
        </section>
    </main>
)
}

export default ProductContainer
